Title: Non-associative geometry and discrete structure of spacetime

Authors: Alexander I. Nesterov and Lev. V. Sabinin

Comments: LATeX2e file, 11 pages, talk given at "Loop's 99 meeting" (Prague,

July 27 - August 1, 1999). To appear in Comment. Math. Univ. CarolineJournal-ref: Comment. Math. Univ. Carolinae, Vol.41,2, 347-357 (2000)

